short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Biscred's browser extension allows users to uncover prospect contact information and company profile details while browsing the web.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Biscred is a sales and marketing enablement platform designed exclusively for commercial real estate. It empowers users to quickly discover new contacts with CRE-specific indicators, and utilize email addresses, phone numbers, and LinkedIn profiles to facilitate connections and close deals.

Biscred's browser extension allows licensed users to easily access contact and company details while browsing the web.
